/// ProlongedSessionMonitor warns users on older devices about long streams.
///
/// On devices with less than 3GB RAM (Tier 1), streaming for a long time
/// can cause the device to overheat or iOS to kill the app due to memory.
/// After 90 minutes (configurable), we show a friendly reminder to
/// consider stopping — unless the device is plugged in and charging.
